{
  "stem": "1917.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 354.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It didn't take very long to die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Dying was very easy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, I decided that I must try to organize some potatoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the following morning, after roll call, when they would choose the person to go to the kitchen-- two of us would carry these 30 gallon containers filled with some kind of a liquid-- usually black liquid that they called coffee.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I volunteered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I jumped high enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I yelled loud enough that I was picked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember that picture so clearly in my mind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And any time I am embarking on something new in my life, that picture comes back to me. 'Cause I was sure-- the rumor was-- again, everything was by rumor-- that if I was caught, I would-- I would be hanged.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If anyone was caught stealing in Auschwitz-- would be hanged.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I didn't know how to steal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know how to organize.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have never done it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was this long, long table with lots of pots, big pots, on it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And underneath, there were a few sacks with potatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I hesitated for awhile.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I said, well, I have got to save her life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Whatever she has, potatoes are the only thing that will help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And I bent down, and I could feel in my hand three potatoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I could almost-- and then somebody pulled me up by my neck, and looked straight in my face-- a woman who was working there-- and said, it is not nice to steal.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I almost started laughing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I thought I was going to be marched out and hanged.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I realized then that to be a Mengele twin, only Mengele could touch us-- no one else.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
